Create a utils folder if necessary. The location is up to you.

Search results must support:
- filtering
- pagination
- sorting (when applicable)

User behavior:

Guests (not authenticated) can:
- view products
- view categories
- search products
- apply filters

Authenticated users can:
- add products to cart
- manage shopping cart
- purchase products

